---
layout: base.njk
title: "투삼로지스 블로그"
permalink: /
description: "위험물·리튬배터리 국제특송, 포장/통관/서류 실무 가이드"
---

<h1 class="page-title">투삼로지스 블로그</h1>

<ul class="post-grid">
{% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
  <li class="post-card">
    <a class="card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
      {% if post.data.thumbnail %}
        <img class="thumb" src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
      {% endif %}
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="card-meta">{{ post.date | date }}</p>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <p class="card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <span class="readmore">자세히 보기 →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
